Wireless Controller<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flex wp-container-7 wp-block-columns\">\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-column\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/amzn.to\/3qWHomt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" src=\"https:\/\/gaminggadgets.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/xbox-one-controller-1.jpg\" alt=\"xbox one controller\" class=\"wp-image-44397\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gaminggadgets.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/xbox-one-controller-1.jpg 250w, https:\/\/gaminggadgets.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/xbox-one-controller-1-120x120.jpg 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"ub-buttons align-button-left\"  id=\"ub-button-c247597a-1b64-459b-880b-5f04df9609f8\"><div class=\"ub-button-container ub-button-full-container\">\n    <a href=\"https:\/\/amzn.to\/3qWHomt\" target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"\n    class=\"ub-button-block-main ub-button-small ub-button-full-width\" role=\"button\">\n    <div class=\"ub-button-content-holder\"><span class=\"ub-button-icon-holder\"><svg xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"height=\"25\", width=\"25\"viewBox=\"0, 0, 448, 512\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M257.2 162.7c-48.7 1.8-169.5 15.5-169.5 117.5 0 109.5 138.3 114 183.5 43.2 6.5 10.2 35.4 37.5 45.3 46.8l56.8-56S341 288.9 341 261.4V114.3C341 89 316.5 32 228.7 32 140.7 32 94 87 94 136.3l73.5 6.8c16.3-49.5 54.2-49.5 54.2-49.5 40.7-.1 35.5 29.8 35.5 69.1zm0 86.8c0 80-84.2 68-84.2 17.2 0-47.2 50.5-56.7 84.2-57.8v40.6zm136 163.5c-7.7 10-70 67-174.5 67S34.2 408.5 9.7 379c-6.8-7.7 1-11.3 5.5-8.3C88.5 415.2 203 488.5 387.7 401c7.5-3.7 13.3 2 5.5 12zm39.8 2.2c-6.5 15.8-16 26.8-21.2 31-5.5 4.5-9.5 2.7-6.5-3.8s19.3-46.5 12.7-55c-6.5-8.3-37-4.3-48-3.2-10.8 1-13 2-14-.3-2.3-5.7 21.7-15.5 37.5-17.5 15.7-1.8 41-.8 46 5.7 3.7 5.1 0 27.1-6.5 43.1z\"><\/svg><\/span><span class=\"ub-button-block-btn\"><